Options description

+-------------+-------------------+-------------------------------------+--------+
| Option Name | Keyboard Shortcut |            Description              |  Type  |
+-------------+-------------------+-------------------------------------+--------+
| gravity     |      g            | Boxes gravitate toward each other   | bool   |
+-------------+-------------------+-------------------------------------+--------+
| ROI         |      r            | Region of Influence - Only consider | int    |
|             |                   | boxes that are within this distance |        |
|             |                   | away (boxes outside this are not    |        |
|             |                   | considered in gravity calculation)  |        |
+-------------+-------------------+-------------------------------------+--------+
| A0          |      a            | If gravity is on, boxes will        | float  |
|             |                   | accelerate toward the center of mass|        |
|             |                   | of the boxes within their ROI with  |        |
|             |                   | magnitude equal to d_CoM * A0       |        |
+-------------+-------------------+-------------------------------------+--------+
| max speed   |      m            | Cap box motion at m px/frame        | float  |
+-------------+-------------------+-------------------------------------+--------+
| bounce off  |      b            | When a box reaches a wall, bounce   | bool   |
|   walls     |                   | off of it. Otherwise, pull a Pac-Man|        |
|             |                   | move to the other side of the screen|        |
+-------------+-------------------+-------------------------------------+--------+
| draw tail   |      l            | Give boxes a tail of length l       | int    |
|   len       |                   |                                     |        |
+-------------+-------------------+-------------------------------------+--------+
| draw ROI    |      d            | draw a circle with radius equal to  | bool   |
|             |                   | ROI around each box                 |        |
+-------------+-------------------+-------------------------------------+--------+
